      <hedline>
        <hl1>Confessions of a Closet Homemaker</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Vivian Owgang letter says Carolynn Carreno's April 3 Live column reminded her of herself and notes she loves to cook for friends0</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>I delighted in Carolynn Carreno's Lives column (April 30). It reminded me of me. I love to cook. For me, it's relaxation. And making special dishes for friends coming to dinner is always a challenge I enjoy.</p>
        <p>Vivian Owgang  Upper Black Eddy, Pa.</p>
      </block>
